rows.label: bf10340100_0010
rows.name: Metsu!

rows.label: bf10340100_0020
rows.name:
Just in time for the final act, boy!
I've saved you the best seats in the house.

rows.label: bf10340100_0030
rows.name: [ML:undisp]...

rows.label: bf10340100_0040
rows.name: Hah, I sounded just like Yoshitsune for a moment there.

rows.label: bf10340100_0050
rows.name: Yoshitsune is dead, you bastard.

rows.label: bf10340100_0060
rows.name: So is Benkei, and Shin...

rows.label: bf10340100_0070
rows.name: Figured as much.

rows.label: bf10340100_0080
rows.name: ...Is that all?

rows.label: bf10340100_0090
rows.name:
What, you want me to weep and deliver a eulogy?
What good would that do?

rows.label: bf10340100_0100
rows.name:
They all desired oblivion,
and now they've achieved it.

rows.label: bf10340100_0110
rows.name: Least I can do is send them off with a smile.

rows.label: bf10340100_0120
rows.name: Metsu... Is this really what you want?

rows.label: bf10340100_0130
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: bf10340100_0140
rows.name: Is this what YOU want, Metsu?!

rows.label: bf10340100_0150
rows.name: I don't understand the question.

rows.label: bf10340100_0160
rows.name: You must understand by now?

rows.label: bf10340100_0170
rows.name: That none of this is your own will!

rows.label: bf10340100_0180
rows.name: Heh.

rows.label: bf10340100_0190
rows.name: You have to see all of this came from Marveni!

rows.label: bf10340100_0200
rows.name: Even if that's true, so what?

rows.label: bf10340100_0210
rows.name:
And don't give me some weak-ass crap
about how I should repent or whatever.

rows.label: bf10340100_0220
rows.name: Why don't you want to hear the truth?

rows.label: bf10340100_0230
rows.name: Here's the thing.

rows.label: bf10340100_0235
rows.name: I don't give a rat's ass what you think, brat!

rows.label: bf10340100_0240
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!!

rows.label: bf10340100_0250
rows.name:
So Blades become Divine Beasts?
And Divine Beasts give life to humans...?

rows.label: bf10340100_0260
rows.name: Honestly, who even gives a damn?

rows.label: bf10340100_0270
rows.name: They can become whatever they want.

rows.label: bf10340100_0280
rows.name:
But that man...
He'd lost everything.
